plonx v0.03

This is you:     @

This is a bomb:  *

Do not hit bombs, or the upper
or lower edges of the map.
Left and right edges wrap around.

You move by using

t y u

f   j

v b n

You move 1-6 spaces forward,
depending on what number you
first pick up on that move.

To quit, press 'q'


